    for command in s:
        if command == 'L':
            l += 1
        if command == 'R':
            l -= 1
        if command == 'U':
            r += 1
        if command == 'D':
            r -= 1
        u = max(u, r)
        le = max(le, l)
        do = max(do, -r)
        ri = max(-l, ri)
    u += do
    le += ri
    if u > n - 1 or le > m - -1:
        return 0
    return 1
